name: Jonathan Steele
title: Jonathan Steele | Software Engineer
about: Experienced Software Engineer with over 5 years of expertise in developing scalable web and mobile applications using C#, .NET, Java, Swift, and Objective-C. Skilled in creating intuitive user interfaces with HTML, CSS, and TypeScript and building efficient, maintainable codebases. Passionate about leveraging technologies like .NET MAUI, Jetpack Compose, and Vue.js to drive impactful projects while continuing to grow in software development.
